<br>
wizards have the ability to quad kite, a characteristic that i believe only druids are able to make claim to.  they are adept solo'ers in outdoor zones.  in xp groups, they are able to provide an extensive amount of damage, and are only limited by their ability to regain mana quickly.  the wizard that regains mana the fastest is the wizard that can cast the most spells.  mana-free damage spell gear (rend robe, velk robe) are extremely valuable to wizards, especially to the raid wizard.<br>
<br>
i feel wizards are a powerful class that tends to be subjected to just porters... similar to a magician, who is generally asked to do coh and mod rod 2 and no more.  wizards bring a great deal of damage, and are one of the deciding classes on raids and encounters that can make or break the battle...<br>
